author: USA TODAY, Elizabeth Weise, USA TODAY
title: Doctors start giving second round of shots to volunteers in Seattle COVID-19 vaccine trial
description: The volunteers who got shots in the first trial of a possible coronavirus vaccine are  getting the second shot — an indicator the trial is going well.
content:
U.S. researchers have given healthy volunteers the first shot of an experimental coronavirus vaccine as anxiously awaited testing opens. The Associated Press observed as the study's first participant received the injection inside an exam room. (March 16)
